data.eml:eml: Two new synonymies in the genus Lispe (Diptera: Muscidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Ge, Ying-Qiang, Gao, Yun-Yun, Zhang, Dong (2018): Two new synonymies in the genus Lispe (Diptera: Muscidae). Zootaxa 4457 (4): 549-556, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4457.4.4
